# ── Python extension modules (pybh) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# The release .so binaries ARE tracked (committed after a stripped release
# build).  Debug builds (e.g. cmake-build-develop) are 10-20× larger and
# must NOT be committed.
#
# These paths are NOT listed here because .gitignore cannot ignore already-
# tracked files.  Instead, skip-worktree is set on each binary so that local
# debug rebuilds never appear in `git status` or get picked up by `git add .`:
#
#   git update-index --skip-worktree \
#     Make/Python/pybh/controller.cpython-312-x86_64-linux-gnu.so \
#     Make/Python/pybh/logs.cpython-312-x86_64-linux-gnu.so
#
# To re-enable staging (e.g. after a release rebuild):
#   git update-index --no-skip-worktree Make/Python/pybh/controller.*.so
/Config/NeuralNets/BallDetector/*.bak_*
/Util/CompiledNN_broken
